USE CASE: 4 Produce a Report of the population in the world who can speak certain languages

CHARACTERISTIC INFORMATION
Goal in Context
As a business analyst, I can run reports to provide the required information of the population in the world who can speak certain languages

Scope
Company.

Level
Primary task.

Preconditions
We know the country. Database contains current language data.

Success End Condition
A report is available for End User.

Failed End Condition
No report is produced.

Primary Actor
Business Analyst.

Trigger
A request for of the population in the world who can speak certain languages

MAIN SUCCESS SCENARIO
End user requests information on populations in the world who can speak certain languages
BA Analyst captures name of the country to get language information for.
BA Analyst extracts current language information of all countries.
BA Analyst provides report to end user.

EXTENSIONS
Language does not exist for requested country:
BA Analyst informs end user language does not exist.

SUB-VARIATIONS
None.

SCHEDULE
DUE DATE: Release 1.0